# ai.list — AI services (LLM chat, APIs, coding assistants) -> AI policy
# Classical rule-set format (rule minus policy). Maintain by hand.
#
# WHY a separate category: most AI providers geo-block by egress IP
# (HK / "unsupported region" nodes get 403 / account bans), so these
# deserve their own policy group pinned to US/JP/SG nodes instead of
# riding the generic PROXY group. Wire as `RULE-SET,ai,AI` (or point at
# PROXY if you don't keep a dedicated group).
#
# Maintenance notes:
# - One vendor per section; keep sections alphabetized-ish and add new
#   vendors as their own section with a date/source comment if obscure.
# - DeepSeek / Qwen / Kimi etc. are mainland-direct services — they
#   belong in direct.list (or nowhere), NOT here.
# - Gemini lives under google.com, so exact DOMAIN entries are used for
#   the AI-specific hosts; don't DOMAIN-SUFFIX google.com here.

# --- Anthropic / Claude (claude.ai = legacy app domain, claude.com = current) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.com

# --- Cursor (cursor.sh = legacy + api2/repo42 endpoints, cursorapi.com = api CDN) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cursor.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cursor.sh
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cursor-cdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cursorapi.com

# --- GitHub Copilot (completions go via githubcopilot.com, not github.com) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubcopilot.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,copilot.microsoft.com

# --- Google Gemini / AI (exact hosts — keep the rest of google.com out of this group) ---
DOMAIN,gemini.google.com
DOMAIN,aistudio.google.com
DOMAIN,notebooklm.google.com
DOMAIN,generativelanguage.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,aiplatform.googleapis.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ai.google.dev
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,deepmind.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,deepmind.google

# --- Meta AI ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,meta.ai

# --- Mistral ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mistral.ai

# --- OpenAI / ChatGPT (oaistatic/oaiusercontent = asset CDNs, chatgpt.com = app) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chatgpt.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oaistatic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oaiusercontent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sora.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,openai

# --- Perplexity ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,perplexity.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pplx.ai

# --- Poe (Quora's multi-model frontend) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,poe.com

# --- xAI / Grok ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,x.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,grok.com
